node.text: Happy birthday to this powerful woman, who is beautiful inside and out, a woman who aspires to be all that she can and uplifts others to do the same. A giver, an inspiration to all who enter her presence, and a phenomenal mother to anyone in need. Today and every day we celebrate you!
